  - ruff `I001` import-collapse (`ruff check --fix` collapses to `from hypothesis import given, strategies as st`).
  - partial-selection coverage-gate FAIL is EXPECTED (`--cov` is in pytest `addopts`, so any partial selection trips the global gate; the `N passed` line is the real signal).
